# OrcheStack root .dockerignore
#
# This file applies to image builds that use the repo root as their context
# (currently just system/auth/Dockerfile). Narrower-context builds
# (orchestrator, dashboard, ge) use their own subdirectory as the context
# and are not affected by this file's exclusions.
#
# The auth image needs assets/css/, system/auth/, and nothing else from the
# repo root. Everything below is excluded from the build context to keep
# uploads small, builds fast, and prevent stray files from leaking into
# image layers.

# ─── Version control ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.github

# ─── Project metadata (repo-level, not container content) ───────────────────
README.md
ARCHITECTURE.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
CHANGELOG.md
LICENSE
CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
SECURITY.md
Makefile
.editorconfig

# ─── Operator documentation (served by Cloudflare Pages, not by images) ─────
docs

# ─── Marketing site (untracked; deployed separately) ────────────────────────
front-facing

# ─── Internal design notes (untracked; not operator-facing) ─────────────────
design

# ─── Test artefacts + release bundles (built by CI, not baked in) ───────────
Test
scripts
*.tar.gz
*.tar.gz.sha256

# ─── Code generators (build inputs, not runtime) ────────────────────────────
_generate_docs.py
index.html
contact.html
services.html

# ─── Python cruft ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.venv
**/venv
**/env

# ─── Node cruft (defensive — no Node tooling today) ─────────────────────────
**/node_modules
**/package-lock.json

# ─── Environment files (CRITICAL: never bake credentials into images) ───────
**/.env
**/.env.local
!**/.env.example

# ─── Editor + OS cruft ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.idea
.vscode
*.swp
*~
Thumbs.db
